  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The apartments are self catering but you can arrange to have a daily buffet breakfast at the Hotel San Giovanni (payable locally). Breakfast at the hotel includes hot choices like eggs and bacon. </p>
<p>There are loads of great restaurants in resort but we have arranged a 15% discount if you dine at the Hotel San Giovanni. They serve up freshly-made soups, pastas, rich meat dishes and homemade pizzas.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The San Giovanni apartments are a great self-catering option. You'll have the luxury of your own space and the option to use facilities at the <a data-udi="umb://document/8b224474a3ec4dc29df4e7081b0fe5e3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8b224474a3ec4dc29df4e7081b0fe5e3}" title="Hotel San Giovanni">main hotel</a>. You’ll find a great bar and outdoor terrace there and get a 15% discount at the restaurant - make sure you try the pizza.</p>
<p>The apartments are located on the outskirts of the resort but you can hop on the free local bus and be in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89}" title="Livigno">Livigno</a> in no time at all. The resort is bursting with great places to eat, drink and shop. Best of all it’s tax free, so your money definitely goes that bit further. Take the opportunity to splash out and make the most of your holiday.</p>
<p>The Amerikan lift is just behind the apartments so you can get a couple of blue runs in before venturing a little further over onto the Carosello 3000 cable car. Once on-board it takes you just short of a thousand metres up the mountain where there's a great selection of red runs and some good off-piste.</p>]]></description>
