  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>San Giovanni Apartments are on the outskirts of Livigno and you can ski back right back to them. The bus stop's nearby and the nearest lift is just around the corner, so getting around couldn't be easier. They're self-catering but you can use the facilities at the San Giovanni Hotel just next door. </p>]]></listingDescription>
